# Origin
 datasets of [GANime-FullBody](https://github.com/HRNPH/GANime-FullBody#ganime-fullbody) project scraped from safebooru website.
and clean with classification model, [method provided below & in github](https://github.com/HRNPH/GANime-FullBody#user-content-data-cleaning)
my goal was to generate full-body anime girls characters in 256x256 resolution

This project is one of the high schooler project from [AiBuilders camp](https://ai-builders.github.io/) graduated student
you can take a look at the model result & code in [Github](https://github.com/HRNPH/GANime-FullBody) you can just copy! (thumbnail image was generated by my model Lol)
I also provide my evaluation process, so it would be a lot better if you can beat it
> ***even if I don't have rights over these datasets, but I hope that you will make your code & process public***

### Note
- at least 16 GB of VRAM is recommended for using this dataset


# Include
- 16k~ of pre-cleaned datasets of Full-body anime girls with no background
- 4k~ of ULTRA-cleaned of pre-cleaned datasets by focusing on simpler clothing style
- Numpy Array of datasets in 32 64 128 256 resolution and additional datasets provided
## Cleaning Method
- using pre-trained classification models, fine-tune on manually classified data
Additional information about [data cleaning](https://github.com/HRNPH/GANime-FullBody#user-content-data-cleaning) provided in github
